title: Vending machines : Market share of product categories in the U.S. 2010
summary: This grouped bar chart shows Market share on the Y-axis for 10 different Food Types for 2 groups 2009, and 2010 that are presented on the X-axis.
Out of all 2 groups, 2010 had the highest Market share for Food Type Packaged cold beverages and 2009 had the lowest Market share for Food Type Bulk vending.
The maximum Market share for 2010 that was found in Food Type Packaged cold beverages was 561.0 times larger than the minimum Market share observed in Food Type Bulk vending.
On average, the Food Type Packaged cold beverages had the highest Market share for all 2 groups 2009, and 2010. Whereas Cigarettes & Cigars had the lowest average Market share.
